title: LF a group of guys/girls in bronze/silver that play flex/normal regularly and enjoy banter!
body:
Hey guys,

This is just a throw away account so don't bother with the rank if you op.gg it.
Looking for a group of guys/girls that play flex or normal's on a regular basis.
Wanna get in on that banter and enjoy the game with some friendly players.

Just comment on this post your IGN or if you have a discord server post that and I'll hit you up.

Cheers!

replies.body: yeah i have a bunch of peeps that are on most of the time, always on disco too, add mi beyb
